<br>
I would suggest sending your cleric a tell first though, and not doing this in the middle of a fight. Nothing screws up the timing of a heal as badly as that trade window popping up =(<br>
<br>
Also I think you would need everyone in the group agreeing to this if you were in a zone that drops gems. As an example if I am in os and half the group is giving me peridots and the other half wants me to loot enough gems to cover the costs, how would I handle splitting up the remaining gems once the costs are covered? <br>
